<h2 class="uppercase tracking-wide text-xs text-slate-800 font-bold">Dependencies</h2>

<p>To add transition effects to components like dropdowns, we prefer an additional dependency called <%= link_to "stimulus-use", "https://stimulus-use.github.io/stimulus-use/", target: :_blank %>.</p>

<p>If for some reason stimulus-use is not installed (check your <%= code 'package.json' %> file.) run the following.</p>

<div class="not-prose mb-6">
<%= content_for :html, flush: true do %>

<% end %>

<%= content_for :js, flush: true do %>

<% end %>

<%= content_for :bash, flush: true do %>
yarn add stimulus-use
<% end %>

<%= render_snippet active_tab: "bash" %>

</div>

<div class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 flex items-center pointer-events-none select-none">
  <%= icon "bell", styles: "text-indigo-600 w-5 h-5", variant: :solid %>
  <p class="m-0 text-indigo-900 ml-2">Stimulus.js and stimulus-use are <strong>already installed</strong> as a dependency of the <%= Railsui::config.theme.titleize %> theme.</p>
</div>
